1
00:00:00,620 --> 00:00:02,060
Greetings everyone.

2
00:00:03,140 --> 00:00:11,240
Today I'll tell about the methodology for determining the push-pull operating frequency for this coil.

3
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:19,360
So wave processes happen in it, heating of this coil happens without load presence.

4
00:00:20,580 --> 00:00:23,240
